<p data-start="1265" data-end="1318">Tempo de carro: ~40 min a 1h (dependendo do trânsito)</p></li></ul></div></div><div></div><div data-highlight-box="true" style="background-color: rgb(240, 253, 244); border: 2px solid rgb(34, 197, 94); border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px; margin: 8px 0px; display: block; min-width: 100px;"><div><b><font color="#dc2626">LOCAL DE EXECUÇÃO:</font></b>&nbsp;<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(15, 17, 21); font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">Principalmente no Centro de Especialidades Médicas (CEM) / Centro de Atenção Integral à Saúde da Mulher (CAISM), localizado na Avenida Humberto de Campos, 70 – Suissa, Ribeirão Pires/SP. Exames de imagem serão realizados nas estruturas disponibilizadas pelo município</span></div><div></div></div><div data-highlight-box="true" style="background-color: rgb(240, 253, 244); border: 2px solid rgb(34, 197, 94); border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px; margin: 8px 0px; display: block; min-width: 100px;"><p><b><font color="#dc2626">PONTO DE ATENÇÃO</font></b>:&nbsp;<br><br><b><span style="color: rgb(15, 17, 21); font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Sim.</span><span style="color: rgb(15, 17, 21); font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font color="#db2777">A contratada é responsável por fornecer todos os insumos</font></span><span style="color: rgb(15, 17, 21); font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> (medicamentos, material de enfermagem, descartáveis, EPIs) e</span><span style="font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font color="#16a34a"> equipamentos </font></span><span style="color: rgb(15, 17, 21); font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">necessários para a realização de exames e consultas. O município fornece apenas a estrutura física e os equipamentos de informática.</span></b></p><ol start="1" style="margin-top: 16px; padding-left: 18px; color: rgb(15, 17, 21); font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-bottom: 0px !important;"><li style="margin-top: 6px;"><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><b>Fornecer todos os&nbsp;insumos&nbsp;necessários (gel, papel, material de consumo).</b></p></li><li style="margin-top: 6px;"><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><b>Alocar&nbsp;profissionais habilitados&nbsp;(médicos ou técnicos, conforme o exame) para realizar e laudar os exames</b></p></li></ol></div><div data-highlight-box="true" style="background-color: rgb(240, 253, 244); border: 2px solid rgb(34, 197, 94); border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px; margin: 8px 0px; display: block; min-width: 100px;"><p><b><font color="#dc2626">DEMANDA É EVENTUAL - TRATA-SE DE UM REGISTRO DE PREÇOS -&nbsp;</font></b></p><div></div></div><p></p><div data-highlight-box="true" style="background-color: rgb(240, 253, 244); border: 2px solid rgb(34, 197, 94); border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px; margin: 8px 0px; display: block; min-width: 100px;"><p><font color="#dc2626"><b>CONSULTA:&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;A EMPRESA VENCEDORA, SERÁ RESPONSÁVEL PELA AGENDA:&nbsp;</b></font><span style="color: rgb(15, 17, 21); font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">A licitante deverá&nbsp;</span><span style="font-weight: 600; color: rgb(15, 17, 21); font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">organizar os serviços médicos em horários distribuídos ao longo do dia</span><span style="color: rgb(15, 17, 21); font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">, conforme a necessidade da Secretaria de Saúde (...). Os serviços médicos para realização de consultas (...), deverão ser disponibilizadas consultas médicas em caráter complementar (...),&nbsp;</span><span style="font-weight: 600; color: rgb(15, 17, 21); font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">incluindo consultas concentradas (mutirões)</span><span style="color: rgb(15, 17, 21); font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">."</span></p><div></div></div><p></p><div data-highlight-box="true" style="background-color: rgb(240, 253, 244); border: 2px solid rgb(34, 197, 94); border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px; margin: 8px 0px; display: block; min-width: 100px;"><p><b><font color="#2563eb">EXAMES&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;</font></b>&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(15, 17, 21); font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">A execução dos exames dependerá de&nbsp;</span><span style="font-weight: 600; color: rgb(15, 17, 21); font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">acesso protocolado</span><span style="color: rgb(15, 17, 21); font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;e autorização prévia da Secretaria Municipal de Saúde, por meio da regulação municipal.-&nbsp;<br></span></span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(15, 17, 21); font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Executar os exames conforme a&nbsp;</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;"><font color="#2563eb">d</font></span><font color="#2563eb"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;">emanda regulada e autorizada</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></font><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(15, 17, 21); font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">pela Secretaria de Saúde.</span></p><div></div></div><p><br></p>PORTAL – BLL - Bolsa de Licitações e Leilões do Brasil  <br>
